    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Savannah, Geo.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><date>Feby. 1<hi rend="sup">St</hi> 1860</date>.</p>
            <p><addressee>Revd. I. Leeser</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia. Penn.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>Dear Sir.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Having established myself<lb/> as a newspaper and General Agent
                in<lb/> this City &amp; beg to apply to act as Agent<lb/> for “The Occident” and any
                other of your<lb/> publications, of which you are desirous of<lb/> increasing the
                circulation in this part<lb/> of the country. My facilities, I consider,<lb/> will
                be unusually large, and prospects<lb/> good, so as to make it to the advantage<lb/>
                of my patrons to employ me. I know I<lb/> will be sufficient, when I say that I
                am<lb/> the son of <persName>Dr. A. H. David</persName> of <placeName>Montreal,<lb/>
                    Canada</placeName>, and nephew of <persName>Revd. Dr. DeSola</persName>.<lb/> It
                is some years since I saw you, but have<lb/> a distinct recollection of having had
                that<lb/> pleasure. An answer, per return mail<lb/> will much oblige.</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">Respectfully and Truly yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <persName role="author">D. David</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <placeName>Whitaker St. near South Broad St.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <placeName>Savannah</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(11)">
                <placeName>Geo.</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
